          div.flex.justify-between.itmes-center
            a(href="/auth/login" class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-semibold hover:text-red-700") ¬øYa tienes cuenta? Iniciar Sesi√≥n
            a(href="/auth/olvidar-password" class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-semibold hover:text-red-700") ¬øOlvisdate tu contrase√±a?

          button(type="submit" class="bg-gray-700 text-lg text-white rounded-md px-5 py-2 my-5 w-full hover:bg-gray-800") Registrar